a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4092104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_4092104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 09, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bvv1665702930308_2.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bvv1665702930308_2.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bvv1665702930308_2.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bvv1665702930308\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      maxlockwait\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__topic_d52205e1_d52206e1_d52207e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__d6874e17\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$Mnmemonic_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= maxlockwait =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">infinite</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__d6874e35\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$Mnmemonic_PARAMS</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">= mlw =</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> { | <code class=\"ph codeph\">infinite</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__section_xkh_lhh_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1130401e90\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__ul_xnj_mhh_jcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__li_d26354e1_d26355e1_d26356e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Seconds</var>—number of seconds to wait\n          for an existing lock to be released; must be &gt;= <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__li_d26357e1_d26358e1_d26359e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>—the application waits forever for\n          the lock to be released. Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">Infinite</code> for MSS. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__section_wqc_nhh_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1130401e115\">Use</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Applies to</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Mnemonic</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Connector Syntax</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Default Value if not Set</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2 connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">DB2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Database-level lock timeout value.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">MS SQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">MSS</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">PostgreSQL connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">PGS</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$PGS_PARAM</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">10</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">SQLite connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">SLE</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$SLE_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Sybase connector</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">SYB</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$SYB_PARAMS</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bvv1665702930308__table_d5330e1_d5331e1_d5332e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Database-level lock timeout value.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__section_njl_m3h_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1130401e328\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__p_d58661e1_d58662e1_d58663e1\">Setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">maxlockwait</span> overrides the\n        database-level lock timeout.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__p_d58664e1_d58665e1_d58666e1\">If the lock is not released after the specified number of\n        seconds, the transaction fails with the following message: <code class=\"ph codeph\">2009 - Occurrence\n          Locked</code>. If <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">maxlockwait</span> is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, the transaction\n        fails immediately.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__section_ulm_43h_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1130401e352\">MS SQL Server</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__p_d48767e1_d48768e1_d48769e1\">If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lock timeout</span> connector option\n        is specified, and it is less than <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">maxlockwait</span> (including\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">infinite</code>), then <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lock timeout</span> overrides\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">maxlockwait</span>. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fje1665702706365.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fje1665702706365.html\" title=\"Set a time-out period for all transaction and query requests.\">lock timeout</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__section_hy2_q3h_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1130401e385\">Example: maxlockwait</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bvv1665702930308__pre_nqd_w3h_jcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS = isolation level:rs, maxlockwait: 5</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zmh1665702705308.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lock isolation</a><p>Set the isolation level for the database transactions of the connector.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kmz1665702706437.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lock level</a><p>Set the Sybase transaction isolation level.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fje1665702706365.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>lock timeout</a><p>Set a time-out period for all transaction and query requests.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iio1665702704280.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Locking Support on DB2</a><p>Full Uniface locking support (optimistic, cautious, and paranoid) is available.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ucb1665702704561.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Locking Support on Microsoft SQL Server</a></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lct1665702664877.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Locking Considerations for SQLite</a><p>The SQLite database has very limited support for concurrency. This has implications for the default locking strategy, hit list behavior, and transaction length.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tav1665702706507.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Locking Support on Sybase</a><p>Uniface provides optimistic and paranoid locking. Optimistic locking is used except when the read/lock instruction is issued. All locking is performed by the Sybase DBMS.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4092104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_4092104\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "maxlockwait Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 09, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 maxlockwait Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released. USYS$Mnmemonic_PARAMS = maxlockwait = Seconds | -1 | infinite USYS$Mnmemonic_PARAMS = mlw = Seconds | -1 { | infinite } Arguments Seconds —number of seconds to wait for an existing lock to be released; must be >= 0 . -1 —the application waits forever for the lock to be released. Use Infinite for MSS. Use Applies to Mnemonic Connector Syntax Default Value if not Set DB2 connector DB2 USYS$DB2_PARAMS Database-level lock timeout value. MS SQL connector MSS USYS$MSS_PARAMS 1 PostgreSQL connector PGS USYS$PGS_PARAM 10 SQLite connector SLE USYS$SLE_PARAMS 1 Sybase connector SYB USYS$SYB_PARAMS Database-level lock timeout value. Description Setting maxlockwait overrides the database-level lock timeout. If the lock is not released after the specified number of seconds, the transaction fails with the following message: 2009 - Occurrence Locked . If maxlockwait is 0 , the transaction fails immediately. MS SQL Server If the lock timeout connector option is specified, and it is less than maxlockwait (including infinite ), then lock timeout overrides maxlockwait . For more information, see lock timeout . Example: maxlockwait USYS$DB2_PARAMS = isolation level:rs, maxlockwait: 5 Copy Related Links lock isolation Set the isolation level for the database transactions of the connector. lock level Set the Sybase transaction isolation level. lock timeout Set a time-out period for all transaction and query requests. Locking Support on DB2 Full Uniface locking support (optimistic, cautious, and paranoid) is available. Locking Support on Microsoft SQL Server Locking Considerations for SQLite The SQLite database has very limited support for concurrency. This has implications for the default locking strategy, hit list behavior, and transaction length. Locking Support on Sybase Uniface provides optimistic and paranoid locking. Optimistic locking is used except when the read/lock instruction is issued. All locking is performed by the Sybase DBMS. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}